message: Hello future player! My strategy focused on consistently achieving a score of 60. First, use the filter tool on any raw non-solid (gas or liquid) ingredients; this reliably creates a valuable liquid. Next, use the vial tool on any raw solid ingredients; this also creates a valuable liquid. The highest scores (60) came from combining ONE 'filtered' item with ONE 'extracted' item. Crucially, ensure both items share the same 'magical' or 'mundane' feature before combining them. Avoid filtering items that have already been 'vialed' as this often leads to 'botched filtering' and lower values. Combining more than two items or mixing 'magical' and 'mundane' features in a single combination often drastically reduces the value, sometimes even below zero. Aim for simple, well-matched pairs. Good luck!

Mixing magical and mundane items or combining too many items at once will reduce your score. Aim for items with a value of 60.
